Instructions

1. Open a NodeJS command line instance
2. Run 'npm install' to add necessary packages
3. After packages have been installed, in same command instance, run 'node server.js'
4. Open a second command line instance and run 'node client.js'
5. Open a third command line instance and run 'node client.js'

NB: The game will automatically authenticate both clients as well as randomly select the choices for each client.